{
  "texts": [
    "We present a comprehensive database prompt construction approach to generate high-quality database prompts.",
    "The strategy mainly contains a schema filter and a value retriever.",
    "The schema filter is to eliminate irrelevant tables and columns based on the given question.",
    "The value retriever is tailored to extract potentially useful database values that align with the question.",
    "In addition to table and column names, we also incorporate various metadata, including data types, comments, representative column values, and information on primary and foreign keys."
  ]
}